HomeCompanyCareers




Careers



At Schnitzer, people have always been a critical part of our success.  With over 3,000 employees working across the United States, Canada and Puerto Rico, we realize that without their hard work, dedication and energy, we wouldn't be where we are today.  As a result, we value our employees highly and provide them with the resources they need to grow and succeed.
There's a place for everybody at Schnitzer.  We encourage a diverse workforce with people from all around the globe, of all ages and job types working well together.  Whether you are just starting your career or are continuing it, new to the industry or a veteran of the industry, entry level or executive level, we have exciting opportunities.  We strive to attract, motivate and reward hard-working people who embrace their work with pride and passion.
Our people share our corporate values, including a dedication to sustainable practices and giving back to the community and a strong desire to do things well and to do the right thing.  They strive for workplace safety, growth and advancement and embrace technology as a way to help accomplish their goals and our corporate goals.

Interested in joining our dynamic team?
Visit the Schnitzer Career Portal today to see the wide range of opportunities we have available across North America.

Schnitzer and its subsidiaries are committed to hiring qualified candidates without regard to race, religion, color, sex, marital status, disability status, national origin or ancestry, veteran status, age, prior industrial injury, sexual orientation, gender identity or expression, genetic information, or any other protected status under local, state or federal law.  We are committed to providing equal employment opportunity with respect to promotion, transfer and discharge; compensation and benefits; and all other terms of employment.
