HomeSell To Us




Sell To Us

Why Sell to Schnitzer?
Schnitzer is one of the largest scrap processors in North America with 43 metals recycling locations conveniently located near major highways, waterways and railroads to provide prompt and cost-effective transportation.  We buy, collect, process, sell and trade a variety of prepared and unprepared ferrous and nonferrous metal scrap.  By selling and shipping to more than 20 countries, as well as serving domestic U.S. markets, we can offer competitive pricing.
We provide superior service to businesses of all sizes and we have expertise in working with suppliers in manufacturing, retail, transportation, utilities, automobile towing and dismantling, construction and demolition.  We bring more than a century of expertise to your job site with the goal of maximizing the value of your scrap, offsetting disposal costs and minimizing environmental impact.

