Sell Your Scrap Metal to Schnitzer


General Public
Sell us your ferrous and nonferrous scrap metal. Competitive prices paid!
LEARN MORE



Businesses
We buy from industrial manufacturers, scrap dealers, contractors & more!
LEARN MORE





Scrap Metal Processing
Scrap Management
Logistics
Transportation
Brokerage and Trading


Schnitzer is a global leader in the metals recycling industry. Founded in 1906, we 
		collect, process and recycle raw scrap metal (ferrous and nonferrous) and provide 
		processed scrap metal to mills and foundries around the world.
Our used auto parts stores provide low-cost quality parts to customers 
		across the U.S. and Canada. Our steel manufacturing facility transforms recycled 
		scrap metal into quality finished steel products such as reinforcing bar (rebar), wire 
		rod, coiled bar, merchant bar and other specialty products.
LEARN MORE






