About SchnitzerInvestorsCareersContacts






HomeCompanySteel ManufacturingProducts




Products

Our state-of-the-art Cascade Steel Rolling Mills mini-mill produces the following high quality finished steel products:





Reinforcing Bar (Rebar)
Used to increase the tensile strength of poured concrete, delivered straight in cut lengths.




Coiled Reinforcing Bar (Coiled Rebar)
Same as rebar but provided in coils, preferred by some customers with automatic straightening and cutting machines.




Merchant Bar (Includes Hot Rolled Flats and Round Hot Rolled Bar)
Used by fabricators and manufacturers to produce a wide variety of products including steel floor and roof joists, safety walkways, ornamental furniture, stair railings and farm equipment.





Wire Rod
Steel wire, delivered in coiled form, used by manufacturers to produce a variety of products such as chain link fencing, nails, wire and stucco netting.


Special Features


MMFX - Our rebar products feature a patented corrosion resistant, high strength technology licensed from our partner, MMFX Technologies Corporation.
Nuclear Quality Assurance - We are accredited to produce steel for use in nuclear facility construction applications.


For More Information


Visit the Products page on the Cascade Steel  site
